## NODE INSTALATION
download nodejs LTS         : Search on navigator nodejs download (Windows), this install node and npm

## NPM INSTALLATION
Installing npm we need one of the version of nodejs must be installed to run (14.x.x >= 14.17.0, 16.x.x >= 16.13.0 or higher 18.0.0)
curl -qL https://www.npmjs.com/install.sh | sh  : Direct download from npmjs.com
npm install -g npm@latest                       : Update to last version of npm
## NVM (NODE VERSION MANAGERS)
If you are looking to manage multiple version of Node.js &/or npm, consider using node version managers https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm

